rows.label: tlk501801_msg0001
rows.name:
Ladies and gentlepon, auction
of today soon beginning!

rows.label: tlk501801_msg0002
rows.name:
Anyone who not yet register for
auction, please sign up quick-quick!

rows.label: tlk501801_msg0003
rows.name:
All participating must bring minimum
of 30,000G! This absolute rule!

rows.label: tlk501801_msg0004
rows.name:
Anyone not having enough golds not
allowed to take part! Would not be
able to win bidding anyway.

rows.label: tlk501801_msg0005
rows.name:
Looks like friends have enough gold.
Now must decide group representative
for bidding.

rows.label: tlk501801_msg0006
rows.name:
Many antique books in auction today,
so suggest friends bring someone who
like that kind of thing.

rows.label: tlk501801_msg0007
rows.name:
If friends not have someone who want
to obtain books at any cost, really no
point in taking part!

rows.label: tlk501801_msg0008
rows.name:
Mo-mo? Me spy budding bidder
with shiny glint in eye.

rows.label: tlk501801_msg0009
rows.name: Maybe today be very good auction!
